Pure Arabic summary text only. No prefixes like "القصيدة تتحدث عن" or chunk markers.

## Core Focus (Priority Order)
1. **Named Entities**: People, places, events (resolve ALL pronouns/kinship using dictionary below)
2. **Primary Theme**: Love/patriotism/praise/mourning (single dominant theme)
3. **Emotional Tone**: شوق/فخر/حزن/غزل (max 2 emotions)
4. **Key Actions/States**: Verbs indicating narrative movement

